      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, an exemplar of automotive excellence maintained to the highest standards. The exterior finish remains flawless, complemented by an interior cabin that retains its original showroom luster. This vehicle has been curated for the most discerning enthusiast, offering a driving experience that is mechanically and aesthetically indistinguishable from new. For those who demand an uncompromising level of quality and a pristine pedigree, this remains an unrivaled acquisition opportunity.",
