    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a truly museum-grade specimen that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with a professionally applied ceramic coating, entirely free of stone chips, swirls, or door dings. Inside, the cabin retains its original showroom aroma; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with zero bolster wear, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive binder of authorized service records and a recent multi-point inspection. From the pristine engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this isn't just a well-kept car\u2014it is a collector-quality investment for the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
