      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in peerless condition, exhibiting the flawless fit and finish synonymous with showroom-fresh inventory. Every surface has been meticulously maintained to satisfy the most discerning collector. Experience an uncompromising standard of luxury and performance in a vehicle that transcends the typical pre-owned category.",
