      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I\u2019ve pampered this car since day one, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Drop me a message and come fall in love with your new favorite car!",
