      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Turbo, featuring the revered 3.6L Mezger-designed twin-turbocharged flat-six. This powerplant utilizes K24 turbochargers for a broader torque curve, delivering seamless boost through a reinforced 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis maintains its original factory-spec suspension geometry, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in and high-speed stability. The AWD system\u2019s viscous coupling is in peak operational condition, providing optimal torque vectoring. With a spotless undercarriage and zero evidence of bore scoring or RMS weeping, this example represents the zenith of water-cooled engineering. A true turn-key investment for the discerning collector seeking peak mechanical fidelity.",
